profile:
ATEL Air has been providing heating, cooling, geothermal, and electrical services to our customers in Kemptville, Williamsburg, Cornwall and Eastern Ontario since 1949.

We provide complete repair, installation, and maintenance services for air conditioners, furnaces, water heaters for homes and businesses.
